vl 20 Mana song  (can't remember the name).  It worked really well for me, and hope it does for you too!  BTW, I also got a key for the second floor for everybody that I grouped with :)</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan="3"><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#9999cc"><td colspan="2" nowrap><b>The Emerald Jungle</b>&nbsp;<font size="1">Type=World Zone</font>|<font size="1">Tag=emjungle</font></td><td align="right" valign="top">|</td></tr><tr><td colspan="3" align="center"><font size="1">No Guide Submitted. Add your own!</font></td></tr></table><br><br><br><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
